{"tid":2033632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我戶口有一舊水 渣BNO 去英國有咩可以搞","createTime":"2020-05-24T18:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T10:10:34.000Z","uid":87428,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"440474e6e8c79dff662fec543aa530684178813f","tid":2033632,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:48:19.000Z","msg":"🤥"},{"pid":"d999b7d934bd7598a48c41a9414f12e24bd352b2","tid":2033632,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:50:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係隧道口吹下saxophone</span>"},{"pid":"98dd9c452934899b1567b4c2bbaad95c49e9c5b1","tid":2033632,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T18:57:08.000Z","msg":"賣屎眼 <br />\n10gbp 一q"},{"pid":"51d90c689b4dc61e2f6fe1716d0f7ac08bd51410","tid":2033632,"uid":348813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T19:09:01.000Z","msg":"去Tesco門口乞錢"},{"pid":"39e1b4332fa37fc062be2677edd80722e1342711","tid":2033632,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T19:11:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BNO平權正視聽</span></span><br />\n連登一向有大量風向L、放負L，睇到BNO平權消息就用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割97後等風向挑撥離間</strong></span>，大家上連登請帶埋個腦。<br />\n<br />\n我從六月開始打英國戰線，希望嚮呢度講幾句。<br />\n第一，BNO平權唔會割97後，因為我地一向都係爭取救<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO及其後代</span></strong>。，除非你係雙非，否則幾乎一定會受惠。<br />\n第二，BNO平權絕對係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同美國行動有關係</strong></span>，故此毫無疑問就係一個救手足之舉，甚至可能與<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">軍事撤僑</span></strong>有關。<br />\n第三，BNO平到權主要唔係用包機包船黎接香港人去英國，亦都冇咩可能會接，畢竟人數太多。平到權最大重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>BNO變正式英國國民，中共逼害英國國民嘅話，英國以至美國就有理由做野</strong></span>。<br />\n第四，BNO平權估計會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寬鬆處理，英屬香港人（BOTC、BDTC、CUKC）無BNO或者已經過期應該都ok</span></strong>。因為英國情報已經判斷香港情況差到似烏干達難民。<br />\n第五，BNO平權大家可以更加無後顧之憂，因為將來要良民證黎移民，可以向英國當局申請。"},{"pid":"8da61ba4ece44fde37531acba7c5579795929680","tid":2033632,"uid":276676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T00:52:07.000Z","msg":"用返賣老翻VCD個招.......英女皇讓位比你"},{"pid":"cc12e187e569af4b344bde4da30e8077b7bb7afc","tid":2033632,"uid":358640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:10:34.000Z","msg":"BNO平權有助香港建立海外屬地 黃色經濟圈全球化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2034495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2034495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}